'''罗伯特·道格拉斯·本顿'''（'''Robert Douglas Benton'''，1932年9月29日—）是一位美国知名[[导演|导演]]、[[编剧|编剧]]和[[制片人|制片人]]。他曾因编剧和执导1979年的经典家庭问题电影《[[克莱默夫妇|克莱默夫妇]]》（Kramer vs. Kramer》）获[[第52届学院奖|第52届学院奖]][[学院奖最佳导演奖|导演]]和[[学院奖最佳原著改编奖|原著改编奖]]<ref name="academy">[http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/BasicSearch?action=searchLink&displayType=1&BSFromYear=52 The Official Acadademy Awards? Database] {{webarchive|url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20160304051957/http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/BasicSearch?action=searchLink&displayType=1&BSFromYear=52 |date=2016-03-04 }}</ref><ref name="Oscars1980">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/52nd-winners.html |title=The 52nd Academy Awards (1980) Nominees and Winners |work=oscars.org |accessdate=2013-04-03 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006094936/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/52nd-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并因1984年的电影《{{link-en|心田深处|Places in the Heart}}》（又译《我心深处》）获[[第57届学院奖|第57届学院奖]][[学院奖最佳原著剧本奖|原著剧本奖]]<ref name="Oscars1985">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/57th-winners.html |title=The 57th Academy Awards (1985) Nominees and Winners |work=oscars.org |accessdate=2013-04-03 |archive-date=2014-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924194841/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/57th-winners.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

